snippet.title: Disorder New Teaser "Ghost Puppet": A Faction That Honors Disorder
snippet.description:
Ghost Puppet is a private military company that profits from the war. They were the first to practice war economy during the world war, and align themselves with multiple belligerent factions like a chameleon. 

Most agents from Ghost Puppet regard war as business and are more like businessmen than soldiers prone to repeatedly changing their allegiance.

What kind of story will this faction bring to us?

Pre-register to join the battle: https://www.playdisorder.com/
